doc.after: The University of Nairobi UON is the largest university in Kenya Although its history as an educational institution goes back to 1956 it did not become an independent university until 1970 when the University of East Africa was split into three independent universities Makerere University in Uganda the University of Dar es Salaam in Tanzania and the University of Nairobi
